data.message:
## Coding Agent 使用说明

### 资产包概览
- **包路径**: `assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/`
- **格式**: sprite_strips（精灵条带，每个动画一个PNG文件）
- **推荐主角皮肤**: `Mask_Dude`（面具小子）

---

### ⚠ 重要缺失资产（需程序绘制）
本包**不含**以下PRD所需素材，必须用 Phaser.js Graphics 程序生成：
1. **敌人** → 用 `graphics.fillStyle(0x00aa00); graphics.fillRect(0,0,32,32); graphics.generateTexture('enemy',32,32);`
2. **管道** → 用 `graphics.fillStyle(0x00cc00); graphics.fillRect(0,0,48,96); graphics.generateTexture('pipe',48,96);`
3. **地面砖块** → 用 `graphics.fillStyle(0x8B4513); graphics.fillRect(0,0,32,32); graphics.generateTexture('ground',32,32);`

---

### preload() 加载代码（完整）
```javascript
// 玩家角色（面具小子）
this.load.spritesheet('player_idle',  'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Main_Characters/Mask_Dude/Idle_(352x32)[frames=11].png',  { frameWidth: 32, frameHeight: 32 });
this.load.spritesheet('player_run',   'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Main_Characters/Mask_Dude/Run_(384x32)[frames=12].png',   { frameWidth: 32, frameHeight: 32 });
this.load.image(      'player_jump',  'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Main_Characters/Mask_Dude/Jump_(32x32).png');
this.load.image(      'player_fall',  'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Main_Characters/Mask_Dude/Fall_(32x32).png');
this.load.spritesheet('player_hit',   'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Main_Characters/Mask_Dude/Hit_(224x32)[frames=7].png',    { frameWidth: 32, frameHeight: 32 });

// 砖块（Box1）
this.load.image(      'box_idle',     'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Items/Boxes/Box1/Idle_(28x24).png');
this.load.spritesheet('box_hit',      'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Items/Boxes/Box1/Hit_(84x24).png',                        { frameWidth: 28, frameHeight: 24 });
this.load.spritesheet('box_break',    'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Items/Boxes/Box1/Break_(112x24).png',                     { frameWidth: 28, frameHeight: 24 });

// 金币（樱桃替代）
this.load.spritesheet('coin_spin',    'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Items/Fruits/Cherries_(544x32).png',                      { frameWidth: 32, frameHeight: 32 });
this.load.spritesheet('coin_collected','assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Items/Fruits/Collected_(192x32).png',                   { frameWidth: 32, frameHeight: 32 });

// 终点标志
this.load.image(      'goal_idle',    'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Items/Checkpoints/End/End_(Idle)_(64x64).png');
this.load.spritesheet('goal_pressed', 'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Items/Checkpoints/End/End_(Pressed)_(512x64).png',        { frameWidth: 64, frameHeight: 64 });

// 背景
this.load.image('background', 'assets/PixelAdventure_1_Free/Background/Blue_(64x64).png');
```

---

### create() 动画注册代码
```javascript
// 玩家动画
this.anims.create({ key: 'player_idle',  frames: this.anims.generateFrameNumbers('player_idle',  { start: 0, end: 10 }), frameRate: 10, repeat: -1 });
this.anims.create({ key: 'player_run',   frames: this.anims.generateFrameNumbers('player_run',   { start: 0, end: 11 }), frameRate: 12, repeat: -1 });
this.anims.create({ key: 'player_hit',   frames: this.anims.generateFrameNumbers('player_hit',   { start: 0, end: 6  }), frameRate: 10, repeat: 0  });

// 砖块动画
this.anims.create({ key: 'box_hit',      frames: this.anims.generateFrameNumbers('box_hit',      { start: 0, end: 2  }), frameRate: 10, repeat: 0  });
this.anims.create({ key: 'box_break',    frames: this.anims.generateFrameNumbers('box_break',    { start: 0, end: 3  }), frameRate: 10, repeat: 0  });

// 金币动画
this.anims.create({ key: 'coin_spin',    frames: this.anims.generateFrameNumbers('coin_spin',    { start: 0, end: 16 }), frameRate: 12, repeat: -1 });
this.anims.create({ key: 'coin_collected',frames: this.anims.generateFrameNumbers('coin_collected',{ start: 0, end: 5}), frameRate: 12, repeat: 0  });

// 终点动画
this.anims.create({ key: 'goal_pressed', frames: this.anims.generateFrameNumbers('goal_pressed', { start: 0, end: 7  }), frameRate: 8,  repeat: 0  });
```

---

### 关键使用示例
```javascript
// 创建玩家
const player = this.physics.add.sprite(100, 300, 'player_idle');
player.play('player_idle');

// 玩家向右跑
player.play('player_run', true); player.setFlipX(false);
// 玩家向左跑（水平翻转）
player.play('player_run', true); player.setFlipX(true);
// 玩家跳跃
player.setTexture('player_jump'); player.setVelocityY(-500);
// 玩家下落
player.setTexture('player_fall');
// 玩家受击（扣血）
player.play('player_hit');

// 创建砖块
const box = this.physics.add.staticSprite(x, y, 'box_idle');
box.setImmovable(true);
// 砖块被撞击
box.play('box_hit');

// 创建金币
const coin = this.physics.add.staticSprite(x, y, 'coin_spin');
coin.play('coin_spin');
// 金币被收集
coin.play('coin_collected');
this.time.delayedCall(500, () => coin.destroy());

// 创建终点旗帜
const goal = this.physics.add.staticSprite(x, y, 'goal_idle');
// 玩家到达终点
goal.play('goal_pressed');

// 背景平铺
this.add.tileSprite(0, 0, levelWidth, levelHeight, 'background').setOrigin(0, 0);

// 摄像机跟随（横版卷轴）
this.cameras.main.startFollow(player, true, 0.1, 0.1);

// 物理引擎配置（Game config中）
// physics: { default: 'arcade', arcade: { gravity: { y: 800 }, debug: false } }
```

---

### PRD元素映射总结
| PRD元素 | 资产键 | 说明 |
|---------|--------|------|
| 玩家角色 | `player_idle/run/jump/fall/hit` | 32×32，Mask_Dude皮肤 |
| 砖块 | `box_idle/hit/break` | 28×24，Box1样式 |
| 金币 | `coin_spin/collected` | 32×32，樱桃替代 |
| 终点标志 | `goal_idle/pressed` | 64×64 |
| 背景 | `background` | 64×64蓝色平铺 |
| 敌人 | ⚠ 程序绘制 | 绿色32×32矩形 |
| 管道 | ⚠ 程序绘制 | 绿色48×96矩形 |
| 地面 | ⚠ 程序绘制 | 棕色32×32矩形 |

